# Project Overview

This is a React Native/Expo project called **guide-ai** that appears to be a travel/guide application with attraction features.

## Tech Stack
- **React Native** with Expo
- **TypeScript** for type safety
- **TanStack Query** for server state management and data fetching
- **NativeWind** for Tailwind CSS styling in React Native
- **Expo Router** for navigation (file-based routing)

## Project Structure
- [app/](mdc:app) - Main application code with Expo Router file-based routing
- [components/](mdc:components) - Reusable UI components
- [services/](mdc:services) - Business logic and API interactions
- [context/](mdc:context) - React Context providers
- [store/](mdc:store) - State management
- [utils/](mdc:utils) - Utility functions
- [lib/](mdc:lib) - Shared libraries and configurations

## Key Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [app.json](mdc:app.json) - Expo app configuration
- [eas.json](mdc:eas.json) - Expo Application Services configuration
- [metro.config.js](mdc:metro.config.js) - Metro bundler configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration for NativeWind
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
